<lb n="1"/>svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> samastabhuvanāśraya śrīpridhvīvalla<unclear>bha</unclear> mahārājādhirāja rājaparamēśvara paramabha
