<lb n="3"/>vīramahēṁdra vikramacōḍa vijayābharaṇa śrīrājakēsarivarmmapermmanaḍigalu gaṁggākā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>vērīparyyaṁta saptamōviṣṇuvarddhanulaina tribhuvanacakravartti śrīkulōttuṁggacōḍadē
<lb n="5" break="no"/>vara pravarddhamānavijayarājyasaṁvatsa 47 śrāhi di 560 ṇḍu gaṁggagoṇḍacōḍavalanāṁṭi
<lb n="6"/>guddavādināṁṭi pedaḍākarēmi śrībhīmēśvaramahādēvara dēva<supplied reason="omitted">dā</supplied>namaina Īyyūri peda<unclear>mu</unclear>
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṁnūṭi Eṟiya<unclear>ka</unclear> kā<unclear>ḍapa</unclear>prōli taṇḍri saṁggavula mēḍaya śrībhīmēśvaramahādēvaraku
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṁ dirumeyibūya jaṁtanamunaku nityapaḍi valamoṁṭiki nani I<unclear>cci</unclear>nami <unclear>viṣuva</unclear>
